author: @MissMayRandomposts
text: Wow, I can see Seungkwan and Vernon are similar..They pick up things fast and get pissed off when they are scared. Even though they already knew this is a horror edition, they still get pissed off knowing what will happen next and keep saying dont do it dont do it..The difference is the assurance after knowing..like e.g when vernon assured that this horror is not that scary he smiled/ or once he gathered his courage, he was no longer scared and acted thick-skinned. But Seungkwan, he goes with flow, constantly feels scared and can be intensified as the time in the horror place stretches. Simply to say, they both are the same but the difference is the compulsiveness levels. Vernon's compulsiveness level is low, controlled/reserved but Seunkwan's compulsiveness level is high. Because of this, we often mistakenly think they are totally different/opposite people even they, themselves (Vernon and Seunkwan )think they are not the same and not compatible because of this. Sometimes because of this, they can be butt head as Vernon prefers to keep things under control while Seungkwan most likely to intensify things (unconsciously)
